title: If you do not wanna become toxic...

embed.description: I moved to LA from Maine with all my things after my military service to hopefully make gaming content that people care about. If you like my videos a sub is all I ask. I had just started playing ranked when I got back from Afghanistan.

body:
Do NOT watch this if you are already a toxic player :) It is too late for you, so instead go and seek medical help!

ps: I share this video, it is not me... Though I think it is very good video!

replies.body: I've found that good music and the mute button work well.
What if I want to become toxic?
So how come you're not diamond OP?
I'm diamond and I am toxic. Confirmed OP is BS.
